Physical abuse is a form of abuse which causes feelings of pain, injury, or other physical suffering. Physical abuse may lead to low self-esteem and other mental problems.


== Types of physical abuse ==
Physical abuse has many forms. A few examples of physical abuse are:
Striking or hitting
Punching
Pushing or pulling
Slapping
Whipping
Striking with an object
Pinching
Kicking
Strangling
Drowning
Sleep deprivation
Freezing
Burning
Electric shock
Cutting
Exposure to a dangerous animal
Poisoning
Withholding food or medication
Assault
Humiliation
Neglect
Biting